{"tid":2349213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深水埗報檔百份報紙被偷走","createTime":"2021-01-01T11:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T13:17:14.000Z","uid":46896,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c6adf111d4b9d18d9255ad0e4aa0794665accd1e","tid":2349213,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"深水埗揭發偷報紙案。凌晨5時許，64歲姓蔡女負責人返回欽洲街27C號書報社開舖時，發現放在門外兩疊、約160份報紙不翼而飛，當中包括《明報》，總值1000多元，懷疑遭人偷走，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，在附近兜截，但沒有發現，將案件列作「盜竊」處理，交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第8隊跟進，正追查賊人下落。<br />\n<br />\n蔡表示，開業至今，報紙已被偷走至少2至3次，對上一次為數年前，對此感到無奈，通知發行再送來。"},{"pid":"5a1a453bf42c01961159566b0b0663e711a64980","tid":2349213,"uid":30040,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:29:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯白分報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c505eac58aa6f661a456e5f31a887f2db3035551","tid":2349213,"uid":33053,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:31:32.000Z","msg":"百分報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f7b70f5976e44553b313593a30d250901640a7","tid":2349213,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:32:41.000Z","msg":"又話百份報 點解係明報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e81ab0a2c1ed3b2947d4b41e61d86e5d61ba90","tid":2349213,"uid":550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:34:28.000Z","msg":"竊報紙不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;竊報紙！&hellip;&hellip;讀書人的事，能算偷麼？"},{"pid":"82d90166fb3fce3e308446e40c13b94a6a328590","tid":2349213,"uid":92125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"偷報紙有乜用？透爐？"},{"pid":"ae41c4a2b880148cfa7b7963131db2837bd433c6","tid":2349213,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:36:32.000Z","msg":"重以為係百份報FANS<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cea153d087ab4c6bd118ce53a405c9d0e958593","tid":2349213,"uid":46896,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"82d90166fb3fce3e308446e40c13b94a6a328590","tid":2349213,"uid":92125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"偷報紙有乜用？透爐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"以前BBQ&nbsp;透爐用親都只係得男極圈果d得2頁紙既來透,<br />\n<br />\n你知啦, 一份報紙得一份鹽濕版, 點會夠用丫...<br />\n<br />\n如果咁岩包炭係濕炭, 你都咪話唔頭痕,<br />\n<br />\n分分鐘落百九幾舊炭精, 火機都用完幾個都燒唔能著d炭,<br />\n<br />\n我都唔係未試過其他方法,<br />\n<br />\n我時不時都唔聲唔聲偷左同事或者家父d 鹽濕版甚至馬經來儲埋來用,<br />\n<br />\n點知有次比唔知同事定家父發現, 屌左我獲金..<br />\n<br />\n唉, 為左透爐連人格都輸埋, 宜家重多左個花名,宜家個個叫我做垃圾仔...<br />\n<br />\n今時今日都重比恥笑梗呀&nbsp;! 真係多得呢班報紙佬唔少!<br />\n<br />\n我諗到嬲嬲地就直踩上去唔知明報定蘋果辦公室同佢理論,<br />\n<br />\n要求佢每份報紙加印多一份特別版鹽濕版, 我連名都諗埋, 叫「每日精損」,<br />\n<br />\n就連計劃書都打埋:「每日精損」係一份為讀者提供中外成人影片最新資訊並附有資深影評..云云<br />\n<br />\n點知, 個個又報以恥笑 + 歧視既眼光望住我, 我當堂無名火起,<br />\n<br />\n正當諗住點著先前預備好縛在腰間既自製炸彈諗住一獲熟既時侯,<br />\n<br />\n其中一個職員遞左份《頭條日報》比我,<br />\n<br />\n我心諗: 做乜鳩... 正當我想用粗口問候佢伯友兼點著個炸彈時,<br />\n<br />\n佢話:你睇左份報紙先講啦...<br />\n<br />\n咪睇我份人好似on99咁, 其實我CE同AL中文同中化 reading 分別都拎 5* 同 A,<br />\n<br />\n所以我用唔夠3分鐘就睇哂成份野, 嘩屌你, 成份野都無內容可言既, 報導唔持平都算啦<br />\n<br />\n重要迫我睇咁多廣告!? 簡直污染我雙眼 !我懷疑佢想用份報紙整盲我然後借機制服我,<br />\n<br />\n正當我又想用粗口問候佢伯友兼點著個炸彈時,<br />\n<br />\n佢又話:係味成份報紙都無內容呢&nbsp;?<br />\n<br />\n我話 :係, 咁又點&nbsp;?<br />\n<br />\n佢又話:咁你咪可以拎去透爐囉! 又唔使錢既!<br />\n<br />\n我即時醒覺 :係喎, 差d忘記初衷添&nbsp;!<br />\n<br />\n跟住我即刻跪係度喊哂口咁多謝佢, 佢最後重親自送埋我落樓添, 所以我到今時今日都重好感激佢&nbsp;!<br />\n<br />\n宜家, 自從有左《頭條日報》之後, 我同家父、同事既關係和睦左,<br />\n<br />\n得閒重可以拎份鹽濕版去廁所&nbsp;J&nbsp;蒼井空添&nbsp;!"},{"pid":"722659b435accfe2d4fc1c8d4d9a024adb41939b","tid":2349213,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:39:57.000Z","msg":"百份報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b528da66e5c06fa3e23ca9528fe6e853436118f9","tid":2349213,"uid":289708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"我以為剩係偷左某一份報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413bda03752c3042dce5c65b7572d9e3846228e4","tid":2349213,"uid":117908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82d90166fb3fce3e308446e40c13b94a6a328590","tid":2349213,"uid":92125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"偷報紙有乜用？透爐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"訓街"},{"pid":"e20d230021a14aabbf61e7c118f93f9a7eb0ea67","tid":2349213,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b528da66e5c06fa3e23ca9528fe6e853436118f9","tid":2349213,"uid":289708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"我以為剩係偷左某一份報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"聽講有份報紙啲道友零舍中意"},{"pid":"9ec31348456cf9946347243c88785964a9e59629","tid":2349213,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2yjLhv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2yjLhv.jpg&h=0859ac3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80e25a9b7f87faf6598e6f69e4ae1783a1acd2b5","tid":2349213,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a1a453bf42c01961159566b0b0663e711a64980","tid":2349213,"uid":30040,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:29:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯白分報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload-review33-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/upload.review33.com/images/201409/201409201258087700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload-review33-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fupload.review33.com%2Fimages%2F201409%2F201409201258087700.jpg&h=f0746bba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26d016a2d2b3f30c1dc154bda631aa8c9c496d15","tid":2349213,"uid":335883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23e81ab0a2c1ed3b2947d4b41e61d86e5d61ba90","tid":2349213,"uid":550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:34:28.000Z","msg":"竊報紙不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;竊報紙！&hellip;&hellip;讀書人的事，能算偷麼？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"接下來就是一些難懂的話：<br />\n君子固窮......者乎......<br />\n<br />\n引得衆人都鬨笑起來：口供室內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"c459257bb6571578e49bd10671f6a626036a7d5e","tid":2349213,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b528da66e5c06fa3e23ca9528fe6e853436118f9","tid":2349213,"uid":289708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"我以為剩係偷左某一份報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"邊份啊~"}]}